OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShetland may
OL,6,Fsee a little light rain at times this
OL,7,Fevening, otherwise dry. Cloudy across
OL,8,FOrkney with some rain and drizzle,
OL,9,Fsome heavy at first across Hoy. A
OL,10,Fchilly night across northern Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry day across Shetland
OL,13,Fwith some bright or sunny spells.
OL,14,FBright spells for Orkney but chance of
OL,15,Fsome patchy light rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,18,Frain clearing on Wednesday. Otherwise
OL,19,Fa dry few days with Orkney seeing the
OL,20,Fbest of the sunshine, Shetland seeing
OL,21,Fmisty low cloud at times. Quite warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
